name: Redeemed PT today (J)
query:
SELECT workflow_state as "Status", pawn_ticket as "New pawn ticket", date_loan_granted as "Date loan granted", desired_principal as " New PT Principal"
FROM `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`
WHERE `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.docstatus=1
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.workflow_state = 'Redeemed'
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.change_status_date = CURDATE()
AND `tabPawn Ticket Jewelry`.branch = 'Garcia\'s Pawnshop - MOL'
